discussing Colin's departure.

00:23.640 --> 00:25.390
- How much?
- Five thousand.

00:25.440 --> 00:27.310
If you threaten my family's future again,

00:27.360 --> 00:29.390
I will hurt you very badly.

00:29.440 --> 00:32.790
This travel card was found
in an office desk of his.

00:32.840 --> 00:34.750
