sort of services you offered.

11:22.820 --> 11:24.410
Just normal.

11:24.460 --> 11:27.930
- Just straight sex?
- Yeah.

11:27.980 --> 11:31.080
Which is what your
friend Samira Khan said.

11:32.140 --> 11:34.530
However, we do now know

11:34.580 --> 11:40.570
