tastes were not that normal.

11:40.620 --> 11:44.900
He both liked to hurt
and be hurt by women.

11:46.820 --> 11:48.690
University College Hospital,

11:48.740 --> 11:52.090
less than 100 yards from
your old Kings Cross flat.

11:52.140 --> 11:56.170
do you remember attending UCH A&E

11:56.220 --> 11:59.250
on 16 February 1990?

11:59.300 --> 12:03.090
The same day, in fact,
